This is why being a business owner, and having actual ownership in companies not licensing , is so important to me and Alex, especially as Latinos. It's about showing our community, this is what life can be. You can take charge and take ownership.

I don t know if you guys know, but Alex and I are part owners in a company called Tiller amp Hatch, and we decided to donate a years worth of of their yummy, healthy meals, for the students and their school s food pantry.
